<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sidebar Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
        }

        /* Estilos del Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 260px;
            background-color: #11101d;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .sidebar .logo-details {
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .sidebar .logo-details i {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .sidebar .logo-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .sidebar ul {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .sidebar ul li {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a:hover {
            background-color: #1d1b31;
            color: #4070f4;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a i {
            font-size: 20px;
            min-width: 45px;
        }

        /* Contenido principal */
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 260px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo-details">
            <i class='bx bxs-bolt-circle'></i>
            <span class="logo-name">Analítica Pro</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-list">
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class='bx bx-grid-alt'></i>
                    <span class="links_name">Dashboard</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class='bx bx-globe'></i>
                    <span class="links_name">Nearshoring</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class='bx bx-transfer-alt'></i>
                    <span class="links_name">Flujos de Carga</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class='bx bx-group'></i>
                    <span class="links_name">Fuerza Laboral</span>
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <section class="main-content">
        <h1>Bienvenido al Panel de Gestión</h1>
        <p>Selecciona una opción del menú para comenzar.</p>
    </section>

</body>
</html>